<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="Learn more about <%= company.name %>'s mission, values, and history of providing affordable technology to low-income individuals and community groups.">
    <title>About Us - <%= company.name %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./public/css/main.css">
    <%- include('partials/favicon-stylesheet') %>
</head>
<body>

<%- include('partials/jumbotron') %>
<%- include('partials/navbar') %>

<!-- Main Content -->
<div class="container my-5 bg-light">
    <section>
        <h1 class="mb-5">About Us</h1>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <p>
                    <span class="fw-bold"><%= company.name %></span> is committed to reducing the digital divide by providing affordable and accessible technology solutions to low-income individuals and community groups. Through the redistribution of refurbished computers, we aim to empower people and promote inclusivity in the digital age.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 text-center">
                <img src="/images/mission.jpg" alt="Our Mission" class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row my-5">
            <div class="col-md-6 text-center order-md-2">
                <img src="/images/volunteers.jpg" alt="Volunteers Working" class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 order-md-1 mb-4">
                <h2>Our History</h2>
                <p>
                    Since our establishment in 1999, <%= company.name %> has worked tirelessly to provide sustainable technology solutions. Our dedicated team of volunteers refurbishes donated computers, giving them a second life and ensuring they reach those in need.
                </p>
                <p>
                    By focusing on sustainability, we also reduce e-waste, contributing positively to the environment.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <h2>Get Involved</h2>
                <p>
                    Join our mission! You can support us by donating your old technology, volunteering your time, or partnering with us to make a difference. Every contribution helps us provide technology to those who need it most.
                </p>
                <a href="/support-us" class="btn btn-primary mt-3">Support Us</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>

<!-- Bootstrap JS -->
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>